    "en": {
      "title": "Restructuring in Sri Lanka Electricity Board",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Power Minister Kanchana Wijesekara said today (04) that the proposal to reorganize the Sri Lanka Electricity Board will be submitted to the Cabinet by the end of this month.",
        "The Minister had earlier informed that a seven-member committee, including former Secretary to the Ministry of Finance, RHS Samaratunga, has been appointed to reorganize the Sri Lanka Electricity Board.",
        "The Minister mentioned that he had discussed the proposals of the reform committee of the Electricity Board this morning (04).",
        "The group has met with development agencies, sector experts, stakeholders and will meet with political parties and the Sri Lanka Public Utilities Commission next week."
      ],
